<br>
If you liked Tribes 2, and aren't much of a lone wolf gamer... you'll love it.  There's just not much room or fun for someone who enjoyes the Lone Wolf role that I could find. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://mywebpages.comcast.net/b_angel517/images/NahrisSig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
