<br>
Multi seater vehicles need not apply.<br>
<br>
I lone wolf quite often in my reaver.  Add an engineering certification and you're pretty much self sufficient.<br>
<br>
But as to the original question.  Yes it is fun.  The fights can get to be enormous.  But just don't get upset if no one works together very well.  Some days I would kill for a squad that worked together well. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.eqfaces.com/photos2/blinkun_copy1.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
